Implementation of Message Passing in Pytorch from easy to hard (step by step)

1. Foundemental flooding test -> 2D, no Multigrid (400 x 400) [Done]
2. Carlisle flooding event -> 2D, no Multigrid (950 x 650)    [Done]
3. South kensington case -> 3D, Multigrid (1024 x 1024 x 128), Linear (one halo layer) [Done]
4. Collapsing water column case -> 3D, Multigridx2 (512 x 512 x 512) [In progress]
5. South kensington case -> 3D, Multigrid (1024 x 1025 x 128), Quadratic (two halo layers) [In progress]
